E. E. JORDAN, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 7305. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Dec. 13, 1933. Edward M. Connelly, of Spokane, Wash., for appellant. Roy C. Fox, U. S. Atty., of Spokane, Wash.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of appellant, ordered appeal dimissed; mandate forthwith.
